		<div class="servings">
			Change servings: 
			<input id="servings" type="number" min="0" step="1" value="1" onchange="changeservings(this.value);" />
		</div>
		<p>
			A few years later I discovered a recipe for a tahini
			protein Smoothie by
			<a href="http://nutritionstripped.com/cinnamon-tahini-protein-smoothie/">Nutritionstripped</a>, 
			one of my favourite food bloggers and sources of
			healthy recipes.  
			I was overjoyed to replicate my Egypt experience at
			home, and adapted the recipe by adding one of my
			favourite spices: cardamon. It turned out simply
			divine.... a mix of chai and tahini in a nutrition
			bomb.   
		</p>
		<table id="steps">
			<caption>Steps</caption>
			<thead>
				<tr>
					<th class="amount" colspan="2">time</th>
					<th>instruction</th>
				</tr>
			</thead>
			<tr>
				<td class="amount"></td>
				<td class="unit"></td>
				<td>Combine all the ingredients in a blender until you get a smooth, creamy consistency.</td> 
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="amount"></td>
				<td class="unit"></td>
				<td>Pour into a glass and garnish with extra chia seeds.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td class="amount"></td>
				<td class="unit"></td>
				<td>Serve cold, and enjoy! </td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<p>
			<q>Cinnamon, spice, and everything nice!</q> 
			This is one
			hell of a raw vegan treat, packed with nutrients,
			antioxidants, and of course, protein.  Rich and
			unusually nutty-flavoured thanks to the tahini and
			chia, this smoothie packs in the protein and essential
			fats. 
		</p>
		<p>
			<b>Macro-tip:</b>To make it lighter, simply skip the banana. 
		</p>
